dialog.body: Hi, I'm having an issue with a billing charge from ABC Gallery.
Hello Brenda, this is Gabriel Cook I'm here to help! Could you tell me more about the issue with the billing?
Sure, I was charged twice for the same painting I purchased last week. I only bought one.
I apologize for the inconvenience, Brenda. Could you please provide me with your order number or the transaction details so I can look into this for you?

Thank you. Let me check our records... It seems there was indeed a duplicate charge. I'll go ahead and process a refund for the extra amount. You should see this reflected in your account in 3-5 business days.
Great, thank you for the help!
No problem, Brenda! Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
